[It is of interest that the source of the index patient's infection is
still officially in doubt. That 19 people have been identified as
being at risk would indicate to this moderator that more is known than
is being shared. Fair enough. Logically a sick cow was slaughtered and
butchered outside of veterinary supervision. - Mod.MHJ]

